Pico 2 active firmware: copper puzzle and final puzzle piece.

This folder name is historical. It no longer runs the dowels/wine puzzle.
Archived dowels/wine code is in:

../../pico-back-room-blender-final/unused-future-puzzles/

Hardware:
- GPIO 15: copper puzzle complete contact
- GPIO 16: final puzzle piece placed contact

